    "text": "Explore\nMore\nJoin Mind Tools\nSign In\nInvest in your career.\nInvest in you.\nFor over 25 years, we've helped people boost their skills to develop happy and successful careers. Join to access our one stop learning hub.\nJoin How it works\nMind Tools topics\nDiscover some of our most popular categories.\nLEADERSHIP SKILLS\nLeadership skills\nWhether you're the leader of a company, a department, a team, or just yourself, having the skills to motivate, inspire and move people to action is essential.\nTIME MANAGEMENT\nTime management\nWith effective time management, you can take control of your time and get on top of your to-do list.\nDiscover newest resources\nWhat is Mind Tools?\nMind Tools offers more than 2,500 resources to help you develop your personal wellbeing and career skills.\n\nTake a tour of the Mind Tools toolkit and find out more about our extensive library of resources.\nHow it works\nWhatever type of learner you are, Mind Tools has something for you.\n\nStill have questions? Our 'How it works' section can help demonstrate how your account would work.\nHow it works\nTrusted, reliable content\nMind Tools learning resources are crafted, written, and regularly updated by our own team of experienced authors and editors, who ensure that every single piece is ethical, nonpartisan, and accurate.\nCreating Mind Tools content\nMember stories\nRead about our learners' experiences with the Mind Tools Club.\nView member stories\nAbout us\nWe created Mind Tools so people like you can achieve their career goals.\nAbout us\nMind Tools popular resources\nDiscover some of our most popular resources.\nSELF-ASSESSMENT\nWhat's your leadership style?\nLearn about the strengths and weaknesses of the way you like to lead.\nARTICLE\nSMART Goals\nHow to make your goals achievable.\nMore popular resources\nJoin Mind Tools\nChoose a membership plan that suits your learning needs. Cancel anytime.\nYou can cancel your Mind Tools membership at any time.\nFor more information, read our Terms and Conditions.\nInvest in your learning with the Mind Tools Store\nExplore our entire range of workbooks and toolkits, and source the skills you need to take your career to new heights. 50% off everything for a limited time!\nVisit Mind Tools Store\n\n\n\nSharon Getz - Mind Tools member for 1+ years\n\"I have recommended it to colleagues and they are now members as well.\"\nRead Sharon's story\nWendy Blackwell - Mind Tools member for 3+ years\n\"Use the Mind Tools Club to support your staff and build relationships with colleagues and your team members by sharing new information.\"\nRead Wendy's story\n\nAn Emerald Works® company\n© Emerald Works Limited 2022. All rights reserved. \"Mind Tools\" is a registered trademark of Emerald Works Limited.\nContact Us | Privacy Policy | Cookie Policy | Terms and Conditions\nCookies\nThis website uses cookies that help the website to function and also to track how you interact with our website. But for us to provide the best user experience, enable the specific cookies from Settings, and click on Accept.\nPreferences\nReject All\nAccept All",
